		{"id":"stack-card","type":"text","text":"## 🛠️ Tech Stack\n\n**Frontend**\n`React` · `react-router-dom`\n`Zustand` · `TanStack Table`\n`Vercel` · `GitHub Actions`\n\n**Backend**\n`Frappe Framework`\n`Python` · `Gunicorn`\n`Nginx` · `Redis`\n\n**Database**\n`MariaDB`\nAzure Managed DB\n\n**Infrastructure**\n`Azure VM` → `AKS`\n`Docker` · `Kubernetes`\nAzure Key Vault\nAzure Firewall / WAF\n\n**PWA**\n`IndexedDB`\nService Workers\n\n**Observability**\nAPM · Centralized Logs\nSmart Alerting","x":840,"y":0,"width":380,"height":720,"color":"6"}
